  "3103280": {
    "name": "DreamWorld: Sandbox MMO",
    "steam_appid": 3103280,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到《梦境世界》，这是一款（真正意义上的）开创性沙盒MMO。世界完全可破坏，所有玩家在同一个无限世界里共同构筑奇思妙想。穿越无穷无尽的奇幻生态区域，收集珍稀资源，进行基地建设与制作，迈向荣耀，与新朋旧友并肩击败世界Boss。包含80小时以上核心内容——更多玩法持续更新中，以及一片没有边界的创造舞台等待你发挥。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103280/extras/7c940cb67bc58f2f06dfbf322406034f.avif?t=1772151211\" width=600 height=116 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103280/extras/7b476304ee4b11d32d5f5ccfea7377b4.webp?t=1772151211\" width=600 height=62 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103280/extras/2f1d2b84f97ea2c0a3287ce52f85378b.poster.avif?t=1772151211\" width=600 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103280/extras/2f1d2b84f97ea2c0a3287ce52f85378b.webm?t=1772151211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103280/extras/2f1d2b84f97ea2c0a3287ce52f85378b.mp4?t=1772151211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >磁吸式快速拼接，自由摆放建筑部件，任意轴向缩放与旋转支持。使用你收集到的任意资源进行建造（数百种材料可探索与制作）。整座城市一键复制粘贴，还可利用游戏内AI即时生成自定义建筑部件。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103280/extras/88fd656a11a488c499423f66b889d08f.webp?t=1772151211\" width=600 height=62 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103280/extras/7a2c38ad82029082115353181897531d.poster.avif?t=1772151211\" width=600 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103280/extras/7a2c38ad82029082115353181897531d.webm?t=1772151211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103280/extras/7a2c38ad82029082115353181897531d.mp4?t=1772151211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从山巅的金色蘑菇，到生长在无尽险恶洞穴深处战场. 每一种生态环境、子生态区、地形变化、昼夜更替，以及你离世界中心越远的每一步，都隐藏着独特而强大的珍稀宝藏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103280/extras/8b26f470342e40adc9a2c8b4ed7ac378.webp?t=1772151211\" width=600 height=62 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103280/extras/015205bd28ba06ac378aff36526a83b9.poster.avif?t=1772151211\" width=600 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103280/extras/015205bd28ba06ac378aff36526a83b9.webm?t=1772151211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103280/extras/015205bd28ba06ac378aff36526a83b9.mp4?t=1772151211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >启动游戏，建造梦想工坊（DreamForge），输入你脑海中的构想。AI会根据文字描述，实时生成自定义建筑组件，供你在游戏中建造使用。作品完全可复制，让所有人都能够欣赏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103280/extras/52aa83f38f8cff513dccb7521ca08d21.avif?t=1772151211\" width=600 height=116 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103280/extras/2f118b6d87c696aef01263cbe562edc5.webp?t=1772151211\" width=600 height=62 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103280/extras/0ffe0a78ad319859039308a70e9d435a.poster.avif?t=1772151211\" width=600 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103280/extras/0ffe0a78ad319859039308a70e9d435a.webm?t=1772151211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103280/extras/0ffe0a78ad319859039308a70e9d435a.mp4?t=1772151211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验超过80小时的核心成长，对抗噩梦敌人，进行基地建设。收集、打造并运用强力武器、法术、地形改造，甚至友情的力量，向胜利发起挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103280/extras/8c936bcdd64c2781d7619e484e967db7.webp?t=1772151211\" width=600 height=62 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103280/extras/fb199edc6139ba8509e075a8d6645c77.poster.avif?t=1772151211\" width=600 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103280/extras/fb199edc6139ba8509e075a8d6645c77.webm?t=1772151211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103280/extras/fb199edc6139ba8509e075a8d6645c77.mp4?t=1772151211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造尽享宁静，想战就战。庞大的共享世界Boss会掉落稀有战利品——如果你能将它们击杀。巨型远古生物在你脚下的土地翻腾，如同潜伏的鲨鱼，随时等待你的动静。深海中的巨兽悄然潜行，陆地上的动物觅食不息。记得准备充分，穿好盔甲。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103280/extras/614a6a40aff4b377ce3cb06cfac63f70.avif?t=1772151211\" width=600 height=116 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103280/extras/271ffdf853d9fbefb495cbfc95d8efde.webp?t=1772151211\" width=600 height=62 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103280/extras/db0b9672a56c4c206430dbec2703ac54.poster.avif?t=1772151211\" width=600 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103280/extras/db0b9672a56c4c206430dbec2703ac54.webm?t=1772151211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103280/extras/db0b9672a56c4c206430dbec2703ac54.mp4?t=1772151211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无需选择服务器来和朋友一起游戏——这里只有一个世界，所有玩家共享。没有混乱，没有分裂，你的梦想、创造、冒险与伙伴，全都汇聚在同一个世界中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103280/extras/5d96cfbefae6beb7b97835ecb9261fc6.webp?t=1772151211\" width=600 height=62 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103280/extras/eaa3f92625a11be5ff38805172f48307.poster.avif?t=1772151211\" width=600 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103280/extras/eaa3f92625a11be5ff38805172f48307.webm?t=1772151211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103280/extras/eaa3f92625a11be5ff38805172f48307.mp4?t=1772151211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《梦境世界》中，没有“基岩”，也没有“建造上限”——只有堆满宝藏的无限洞穴和广阔美丽的天空。收集你看到的一切，建造任何东西，挖掉整座山或铺设它，夷平或种植一片森林，与社区分享坐标，随时随地展示你的创意，吸引成千上万玩家。如果你想要的工具还不存在，可以去我们的 Discord 留言，我们会帮你加入。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103280/extras/b96578d59ee14f94a65798a96f2dd2e9.webp?t=1772151211\" width=600 height=62 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103280/extras/cb681de649aad6ab8a58f833e008637c.poster.avif?t=1772151211\" width=600 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103280/extras/cb681de649aad6ab8a58f833e008637c.webm?t=1772151211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103280/extras/cb681de649aad6ab8a58f833e008637c.mp4?t=1772151211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个无限延展的世界里，移动本身就是力量。你可以攀登任何表面，潜入任意深度，飞向天际尽头。与友善的坐骑一同穿越奇异而梦幻的地形。这里没有“仅供观赏的场景”，没有看不见的空气墙，也没有所谓的“限制区域”。真正的自由，没有边界。</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 法语<strong>*</strong>, 意大利语<strong>*</strong>, 德语<strong>*</strong>, 西班牙语 - 西班牙<strong>*</strong>, 阿拉伯语<strong>*</strong>, 印度尼西亚语<strong>*</strong>, 日语<strong>*</strong>, 韩语<strong>*</strong>, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西<strong>*</strong>, 俄语<strong>*</strong>, 简体中文<strong>*</strong>, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲<strong>*</strong>, 繁体中文<strong>*</strong>, 土耳其语<strong>*</strong>, 保加利亚语<strong>*</strong>, 捷克语<strong>*</strong>, 丹麦语<strong>*</strong>, 荷兰语<strong>*</strong>, 芬兰语<strong>*</strong>, 希腊语<strong>*</strong>, 匈牙利语<strong>*</strong>, 挪威语<strong>*</strong>, 波兰语<strong>*</strong>, 葡萄牙语 - 葡萄牙<strong>*</strong>, 罗马尼亚语<strong>*</strong>, 瑞典语<strong>*</strong>, 泰语<strong>*</strong>, 乌克兰语<strong>*</strong>, 越南语<strong>*</strong>, 印地语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
